OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome brightness across the east
OL,6,Fthis morning. Otherwise a mostly dry
OL,7,Fand rather cloudy day with the odd
OL,8,Flight shower this morning. A few
OL,9,Fbright spells may develop by late
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,13,Fsome late brightness. Then the rest of
OL,14,Fthe night will be largely dry but some
OL,15,Frain spreading into Galloway later.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FOutbreaks of rain will
OL,18,Fspread east across all parts during
OL,19,Fthe morning. Then bright spells and
OL,20,Fscattered showers following on for the
OL,21,Fafternoon. Colder than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
